 Galvatron saw the battle at the cf come in view. He landed behind the preds 
about 30 feet behind. He sent a comm to Zardus. "We have arrived. I will 
attack froiom behind. With all the comotion they have not seen me. When my 
men surprise attack from behind the temporary disturbance should allow you to 
turn thier flank on thier right. Leaving and opening for the rest of 
darkfates troops to arrive and surrond them." he sent this in triple code.

--part1_53.29ba21a.27c4060d_boundary
